|4 |    │ └─SUBPLAN SCAN                       |v       |1       |23          |
|5 |    │   └─HASH GROUP BY                    |        |1       |23          |
|6 |    │     └─HASH JOIN                      |        |1       |23          |
|7 |    │       ├─JOIN FILTER CREATE           |:RF0000 |1       |12          |
|8 |    │       │ └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |1       |12          |
|9 |    │       │   └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)|:EX10000|1       |11          |
|10|    │       │     └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |1       |11          |
|11|    │       │       └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t1      |1       |11          |
|12|    │       └─EXCHANGE IN DISTR            |        |1       |11          |
|13|    │         └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH)  |:EX10001|1       |11          |
|14|    │           └─JOIN FILTER USE          |:RF0000 |1       |11          |
|15|    │             └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |1       |11          |
|16|    │               └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t2      |1       |11          |
